data.description: This beautiful lakefront home is nestled on a private cul-de-sac with screened-in private pool & patio area that's perfect for entertaining. Located in a gated community, this spacious split floor plan offers 3BR, 2BA, & 2-car garage. The home has numerous upgrades, including tile throughout all living areas, vaulted ceilings, upgraded kitchen with stainless-steel appliances, granite countertops, electric blinds in living & breakfast rooms & much more. The home offers an oversized lot, covered back patio w/mounted TV, inground pool, fully screened pool/patio area, & a fenced backyard with a scenic lake view.  With a new custom paver patio & a beautiful fireplace, you'll enjoy breathtaking lake views and beautiful sunsets year-round. This property is the epitome of Florida living. The backyard is a paradise with a variety of fruit trees, including banana, grapefruit, orange, lime, mangoes, avocados & pineapple plants. You can fish on lake and 10' boats with electric trolling motors allowed on lake. New roof in 2018;refrigerator, garbage disposal, microwave, hot water heater in 2021; new tile in lanai in 2022; custom paver patio and fireplace in 2023; new pool sand filter 2023; new irrigation pump 2023. HOA is $447 quarterly and includes cable and internet.
